  "title": "Restaurant Supervisor | $3000 - $3500",
  "description": "<h2>Restaurant Supervisor (Semi-Fine Dining)</h2><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $3,000 – $3,500<br /><strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-time<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br /><strong>Working Days:</strong> 5 days work week (including weekends & public holidays)<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Shift-based </p><h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are seeking a service-oriented and detail-driven <strong>Restaurant Supervisor</strong> to support daily operations in a semi-fine dining environment. The ideal candidate will lead the service team, uphold refined service standards, and ensure an exceptional dining experience for all guests.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Supervise and coordinate Front of House (FOH) service operations during shifts</p></li><li><p>Lead, coach, and motivate service staff to deliver attentive and professional service</p></li><li><p>Ensure service standards, presentation, and guest interactions meet semi-fine dining expectations</p></li><li><p>Handle guest feedback, requests, and service recovery with professionalism and confidence</p></li><li><p>Assist with training and mentoring of new and junior service staff</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with food safety, hygiene, and operational SOPs</p></li><li><p>Coordinate closely with kitchen and management teams for smooth service flow</p></li><li><p>Oversee opening and closing procedures when required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>1–2 years of experience</strong> in a semi-fine dining or upscale restaurant environment</p></li><li><p>Prior supervisory or senior service role experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Calm, professional, and service-focused under pressure</p></li><li><p>Well-groomed and attentive to detail</p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of service etiquette, wine basics, or POS systems is an advantage</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary</p></li><li><p>Structured service standards and training</p></li><li><p>Staff meals and employee benefits (where applicable)</p></li><li><p>Professional and supportive working environment<br /><br /></p><p>Daniel Ng (R25126885)<br />Hey Rocket Pte Ltd (EA 21C0816)</p></li></ul>",
